# 成都各年建成小区数量分布

plt.title = 'Second_hand housing build time in chengdu'
plt.xlabel(r'$bulid\ year$')
plt.ylabel(r'$count$')
plt.xlim(1900,2021)
X,Y = [],[]
for x,y in df.buildtime.value_counts().sort_index().iteritems():
    plt.text(int(x),y+25,y,ha='center',va='bottom')
    X.append(int(x))
    Y.append(y)
l = plt.plot(X,Y,'r-',label='community_count')
plt.plot(X,Y,'ro-')

plt.legend()
plt.show()

#线的粗细
plt.rcParams['lines.linewidth'] = 2
#x轴的大小
plt.rcParams['xtick.labelsize'] = 14
#y轴的大小
plt.rcParams['ytick.labelsize'] = 14
#图例大小

#图的大小

count = []

    count.append(item)
explode = (0, 0,0.5) 
color = ['cornflowerblue', 'orange', 'limegreen']
plt.figure(figsize=(20, 8))
plt.pie(count, labels = df.structure.value_counts().index,radius=1,autopct='%2.2f%%',textprops={'fontsize':13,'color':'w'}
        ,explode = explode,shadow=True,startangle=20,pctdistance = 0.8)
plt.axis('equal')
plt.legend()

#pctdistance,百分比的文本离圆心的距离为0.8

# 打开百度地图api获取每个小区经纬度,百度地图的api不怎么稳定，运行了多次才把所有地址经纬度找到
import requests
import ast
import pymysql
conn = connect(host='localhost',port=3306,user='root',password='root',database='spiderdata',charset='utf8')
df = pd.read_sql('select * from beikedata_community1',con=conn)
lng = pd.read_sql('select id,longitude from beikedata_community1',con=conn)
df.fillna(0,inplace=True)
count = 0
with conn.cursor() as cur:
    for i,j,k in zip(df.id,df.name,df.area):
        if float(df.loc[df['id']==i]['longitude'])==0:
            print(i)
            try:
                r = requests.get('http://api.map.baidu.com/geocoder?address={}&output=json&key=QFETilCraadFXYbiX11sgtOIaZtCOOe5&city={}'.format(j,k))
                longitude = ast.literal_eval(r.text)['result']['location']['lng']
                latitude = ast.literal_eval(r.text)['result']['location']['lat']
                cur.execute('update beikedata_community1 set longitude=%s,latitude=%s where id=%s',(longitude,latitude,i))
            except Exception as e:
                print(e)
                print(df.loc[df['id']==i]['area'])
                count += 1
            else:
                conn.commit()
print('还有{}个地址没有经纬度'.format(count))
conn.close()

#由于没有指定上级地址，高新区与天府新区匹配了许多错误的坐标，超出成都范围需要重新获取
import requests
import ast
from pymysql import *
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
conn = connect(host='localhost',port=3306,user='root',password='root',database='spiderdata',charset='utf8')
df = pd.read_sql('select * from beikedata_community1',con=conn)
df.fillna(0,inplace=True)
pending= [i for i,j in zip(df.id,df.area) if  j=='天府新区']
print('待处理地址{}个'.format(len(pending)))
df.set_index('id',inplace=True)#把id设置为索引
count = 0
with conn.cursor() as cur:
    while len(pending)>0:
        for i in pending:
            j = df.at[i,'position']
            k = '成都'+ df.at[i,'area']
            
            try:
                r = requests.get('http://api.map.baidu.com/geocoder?address={}&output=json&key=QFETilCraadFXYbiX11sgtOIaZtCOOe5&city={}'.format(j,'成都市'))
                longitude = ast.literal_eval(r.text)['result']['location']['lng']
                latitude = ast.literal_eval(r.text)['result']['location']['lat']
                cur.execute('update beikedata_community1 set longitude=%s,latitude=%s where id=%s',(longitude,latitude,i))
            except Exception as e:
                print(e,j)
            else:
                conn.commit()
                pending.remove(i)
                print('还有{}个待处理'.format(len(pending)))
            

        count += 1
conn.close()
